<div id="content" lang="en" dir="ltr">
<em><strong>No Spoilers here, please.</strong></em> <p>
Half-Ogres are a crossbreed between a human and an ogre. They are big, bad, and  stupid. For warriors, they have all the necessary attributes, and they can even become priests: after all, they are related to Ogre Magi, from whom they have learned the skill of setting trapped runes once their level is high enough. Like Orcs, they resist darkness, and like Trolls, they have their strength sustained. 
</p>
<p>
Stat Modifiers: 
